n real-time, and can be adjusted after recording is complete. Starting and stopping a loop is as simple as striking a ringer, extending EXA\u2019s musical possibilities even further.<br><br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/606920/extras/LoopRecorder.png?t=1511188526\" >",
